      "parameters": {
        "content": "## DSC-GCP-DAG-List-Sync-v1\n**Purpose:** Daily sync \u2014 drops and recreates SRE_Supported_Composer_Dags data table, reloads from Google Sheet, then records the new table ID in the registry.\n**Trigger:** Daily schedule (6:00 AM UTC)\n**Sheet credential:** SRE team Google Sheets Oauth (id: aY5cxQ8CpL83zdck)\n**HTTP nodes:** No credentials set \u2014 configure tzago-n8n-api-key via Header Auth in the n8n UI after deploy.\n**Owner:** CIO DataHub SRE team",
        "height": 150,
        "width": 1800,
        "color": 0
      },
      "id": "sticky-overview",
      "name": "Overview",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
